1
00:00:15,480 --> 00:00:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey there. Is Eraser around?</font>

2
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:21,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a report on my 
recent patrols for him.</font>

3
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's not here today.</font>

4
00:00:23,870 --> 00:00:26,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's been working with 
the cops a lot lately.</font>

5
00:00:26,660 --> 00:00:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, I thought that kinda 
stuff was Midnight's thing?</font>

6
00:00:30,330 --> 00:00:32,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe you should ask her to come over...</font>

7
00:00:32,590 --> 00:00:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, I'd feel bad interrupting 
someone when they're working.</font>

8
00:00:36,380 --> 00:00:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you don't mind coming here and 
interrupting us when we're working?</font>

9
00:00:39,430 --> 00:00:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, Pop is the one who gets 
along with Midnight, so...</font>

10
00:00:43,300 --> 00:00:45,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it, where is she?</font>

11
00:00:46,260 --> 00:00:49,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's been getting ready for the 
Captain's farewell event around the clock.</font>

12
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:52,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, the Captain Celebrity thing.</font>

13
00:00:52,350 --> 00:00:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's gonna be at the Sky Egg, 
right? Sounds like a big deal.</font>

14
00:00:55,770 --> 00:00:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gonna be helping out with it?</font>

15
00:00:58,290 --> 00:01:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They said I'd just get in the way 
and asked me to not get involved.</font>

16
00:01:02,420 --> 00:01:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I get it.</font>

17
00:01:04,540 --> 00:01:07,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, don't really see 
you being much help.</font>

18
00:02:39,340 --> 00:02:46,390
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an1}<font size="40"><font color="#c5000e">[Catastrophe]</font></font></b></font>

19
00:02:41,300 --> 00:02:46,390
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an7}Great upheaval in society or the natural world.
 Major change.
 Can also refer to a tragic outcome in stories.
Often accompanied by destruction.</b></font>

20
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:47,390
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b><i>{\an1}<font size="30"><font color="#ffe640">Zero Hour</font></font></i></b></font>

21
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:53,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regarding the record of the vigilantes' 
activities you gave me the other day.</font>

22
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get right to the point: 
it's come in incredibly handy,</font>

23
00:02:57,540 --> 00:03:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and provided us with a vital lead.</font>

24
00:03:00,990 --> 00:03:03,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By taking the small-time 
criminals noted in it,</font>

25
00:03:03,850 --> 00:03:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">along with the personal information 
of the instant villain victims,</font>

26
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:09,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and indexing it with the customer 
list from Hong Kong...</font>

27
00:03:09,740 --> 00:03:14,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've got a list of individuals who would
fall into "friend of a friend" territory,</font>

28
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for both the villain attacks 
and the drug operations.</font>

29
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But half of them are involved with a
mid-sized pharmaceutical company,</font>

30
00:03:24,630 --> 00:03:28,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onomura Pharma Corp, as either 
employees or contractors.</font>

31
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onomura... doesn't ring a bell.</font>

32
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's their deal?</font>

33
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the most part, they produce and 
sell drugs wholesale to hospitals,</font>

34
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which is why they're not particularly 
well known to the public.</font>

35
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They may be the Factory's 
base of operations...</font>

36
00:03:42,670 --> 00:03:45,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if not that, one of 
their other hideouts.</font>

37
00:03:45,490 --> 00:03:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, we're getting closer 
to the root of the operation.</font>

38
00:03:51,770 --> 00:03:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't say I'm thrilled as a police 
officer to have to rely so heavily</font>

39
00:03:57,990 --> 00:04:02,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">on anonymous tips, but...</font>

40
00:04:02,050 --> 00:04:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, when it comes to that—</font>

41
00:04:04,510 --> 00:04:06,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fuhgeddaboutit!</font>

42
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's it matter where the tip comes from?</font>

43
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:12,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it gets results, then that's 
that! Who cares about the source?</font>

44
00:04:12,140 --> 00:04:14,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the whole rational thing!</font>

45
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ain't that right, big guy?</font>

46
00:04:17,050 --> 00:04:20,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we have our reinforcements 
from Osaka...</font>

47
00:04:20,370 --> 00:04:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The BMI Hero, Fatgum.</font>

48
00:04:23,100 --> 00:04:24,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meetcha.</font>

49
00:04:24,490 --> 00:04:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm with Osaka PD! The name's 
Kaniyashiki! You can call me Kaniko.</font>

50
00:04:28,570 --> 00:04:29,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello there.</font>

51
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Officer Kaniyashiki has been 
working on the investigation</font>

52
00:04:33,050 --> 00:04:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to nail down the drug trafficking routes.</font>

53
00:04:35,100 --> 00:04:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fatgum is...</font>

54
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here as a precaution, in the event of 
more altered villain combat, I take it?</font>

55
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got it!</font>

56
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:46,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This luscious bod o' mine's basically 
invulnerable to impacts!</font>

57
00:04:46,470 --> 00:04:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it turns into a slobberknocker,
I can handle it!</font>

58
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:54,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Up 'til now, I handled the investigating 
and Fatyan was the muscle—</font>

59
00:04:54,690 --> 00:04:57,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if a villain pops outta nowhere,</font>

60
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there's no telling if I can 
hit the scene in time.</font>

61
00:04:59,610 --> 00:05:02,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got in a real mess the other 
day because of that!</font>

62
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it ain't like I can 
back her up all the time.</font>

63
00:05:06,060 --> 00:05:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A frame like mine isn't a good match for 
sneaking around or wearing disguises!</font>

64
00:05:10,290 --> 00:05:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's where you come in, big guy!</font>

65
00:05:13,330 --> 00:05:17,790
<font face="Arial Black" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#0f0a0d">Investigation</font></b></font>

66
00:05:13,590 --> 00:05:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eraser, we'd like you to 
accompany Officer Kaniyashiki</font>

67
00:05:14,330 --> 00:05:19,790
<font face="Arial Black" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#112330">Combat & Investigation</font></b></font>

68
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as an investigator with combat potential.</font>

69
00:05:17,290 --> 00:05:19,790
<font face="Arial Black" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#0c0800">Combat</font></b></font>

70
00:05:19,790 --> 00:05:22,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be backing you two up,</font>

71
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it'd be a relief 
knowing we've got someone</font>

72
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who can handle a scrap 
on the scene already.</font>

73
00:05:25,610 --> 00:05:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm thrilled to be working 
with such a handsome fella!</font>

74
00:05:28,010 --> 00:05:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that mean you're always 
thrilled to be working with me?</font>

75
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What're you talking about, porky?</font>

76
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, big guy, say something!</font>

77
00:05:38,730 --> 00:05:41,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This don't look good, Fatyan! 
He's not playing along at all.</font>

78
00:05:41,730 --> 00:05:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I gonna be able to work with him?</font>

79
00:05:43,330 --> 00:05:46,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe you oughta act like an 
even bigger goof than usual?</font>

80
00:05:46,570 --> 00:05:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What're you yappin' about?</font>

81
00:05:47,970 --> 00:05:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My best schtick, the Heike Crab face, only
works when I'm playin' the straight man!</font>

82
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It ain't funny enough to work 
as a punchline, anyway.</font>

83
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes it freakin' is!</font>

84
00:05:56,780 --> 00:05:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, you little...</font>

85
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:02,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wanna get snipped?! I can snip ya!</font>

86
00:06:02,530 --> 00:06:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Snip ya real good!</font>

87
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:05,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you want me to get in on that?</font>

88
00:06:05,050 --> 00:06:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not exactly.</font>

89
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:20,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="20"><b>{\an7}<font color="#000203">Naruhata x Hong Kong

Onomura Pharma

<font size="15">\h\h\h\h\h\hKaniyashiki
\h\h\h\h\h\hEraser
\h\h\h\h\h\hFatgum</font></font></b></font>

90
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In summary, we're going to be 
working with other departments</font>

91
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to investigate Onomura Pharma.</font>

92
00:06:15,330 --> 00:06:18,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The three of you will be 
responsible for direct contact</font>

93
00:06:18,130 --> 00:06:20,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with a number of their employees.</font>

94
00:06:20,150 --> 00:06:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a dangerous role, considering the
chances of encountering a villain, but...</font>

95
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:28,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if one does actually show up...</font>

96
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:30,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That keeps things nice and simple, right?</font>

97
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:31,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

98
00:06:31,650 --> 00:06:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alright, let's start digging!</font>

99
00:06:33,610 --> 00:06:35,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look lively, folks!</font>

100
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The suit looks nice on you.</font>

101
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why am I stuck wearing this...?</font>

102
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, think of it as practice.</font>

103
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:49,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you get into hot water in the future, 
you'll hafta apologize in one of those!</font>

104
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is not going to happen—</font>

105
00:06:50,140 --> 00:06:52,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get a move on! Excuse me!</font>

106
00:06:54,380 --> 00:06:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, why all the dressing up?</font>

107
00:06:57,180 --> 00:06:58,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, it's fine!</font>

108
00:06:58,940 --> 00:07:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why, though...?</font>

109
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine, trust me!</font>

110
00:07:03,810 --> 00:07:05,480
<font face="Arial Black" size="20"><b><font color="#cf4a4c">Store Open</font></b></font>

111
00:07:03,970 --> 00:07:04,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

112
00:07:04,870 --> 00:07:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine! Fine, fine, fine!</font>

113
00:07:11,690 --> 00:07:13,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And bingo.</font>

114
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:13,820
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#0c0800">Entry pass</font></b></font>

115
00:07:19,350 --> 00:07:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

116
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:22,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That hair...</font>

117
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:25,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is Kaniko!</font>

118
00:07:25,770 --> 00:07:28,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know she was in Tokyo.</font>

119
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it for Kanidoke business?</font>

120
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the person she's with...</font>

121
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:37,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eraser? Does he know her?</font>

122
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, it's a small world.</font>

123
00:07:41,090 --> 00:07:44,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A few of the girls don't have 
the choreography down yet,</font>

124
00:07:44,410 --> 00:07:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the dance club captain is providing 
them with individual coaching...</font>

125
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're ordering new costumes?!</font>

126
00:07:51,770 --> 00:07:55,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we'll have to get everyone's 
measurements at the next practice!</font>

127
00:07:56,230 --> 00:07:59,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, the sooner the better? Understood!</font>

128
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll call the others and get back to you.</font>

129
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:03,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back.</font>

130
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you wouldn't believe 
who I saw in town...</font>

131
00:08:06,460 --> 00:08:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, but I need to make 
some urgent calls for Makoto!</font>

132
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

133
00:08:11,580 --> 00:08:16,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yu? It's Pop! I was hoping to get your 
measurements for our new costumes...</font>

134
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! Same for Miu, right?</font>

135
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:23,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, see you at practice!</font>

136
00:08:25,250 --> 00:08:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dude, what are you doing here? 
It's not like you need anything.</font>

137
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:32,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Pop seemed really busy, and 
I didn't wanna get in her way...</font>

138
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:35,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Again, how does that justify 
getting in our way?</font>

139
00:08:35,770 --> 00:08:38,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, Eraser finally stopped 
dropping in all the time,</font>

140
00:08:38,260 --> 00:08:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now we've gotta deal with this guy.</font>

141
00:08:40,420 --> 00:08:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, actually, speaking of Eraser...</font>

142
00:08:43,870 --> 00:08:46,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean he was 
going around with a chick?!</font>

143
00:08:46,410 --> 00:08:48,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know her, too, by the way.</font>

144
00:08:48,820 --> 00:08:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, who is she?!</font>

145
00:08:51,070 --> 00:08:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

146
00:08:52,860 --> 00:08:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The official idol of the Kanidoke!</font>

147
00:08:58,290 --> 00:09:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. It's been a while.</font>

148
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything new to report?</font>

149
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll also take a coffee. Black.</font>

150
00:09:04,090 --> 00:09:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eraser!</font>

151
00:09:05,170 --> 00:09:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're dating a frickin' idol?!</font>

152
00:09:07,210 --> 00:09:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For real?!</font>

153
00:09:08,140 --> 00:09:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you! I am so jealous!</font>

154
00:09:11,210 --> 00:09:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

155
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:16,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who cares?! Set up a mixer with us!</font>

156
00:09:16,150 --> 00:09:18,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We wanna meet idols!</font>

157
00:09:29,610 --> 00:09:35,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Welcome to the final Captain Celebrity 
stage show at the Tokyo Sky Egg.</i></font>

158
00:09:35,890 --> 00:09:41,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Attendees with tickets are asked to 
please line up at the entrance gate.</i></font>

159
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've got merch over here!</font>

160
00:09:43,410 --> 00:09:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take a hoodie!</font>

161
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take a fan, and a towel, and...</font>

162
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two copies of the program.</font>

163
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here they come!</font>

164
00:10:18,810 --> 00:10:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here they come.</font>

165
00:10:23,700 --> 00:10:24,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here they come!</font>

166
00:10:28,650 --> 00:10:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here they come!</font>

167
00:10:32,180 --> 00:10:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here they come!</font>

168
00:10:36,020 --> 00:10:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wash!</font>

169
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fastest!</font>

170
00:10:38,930 --> 00:10:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The strongest!</font>

171
00:10:40,210 --> 00:10:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The most illustrious!</font>

172
00:10:41,970 --> 00:10:47,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Competing to see whose Quirk shines
brightest, Japan's greatest heroes!</font>

173
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:51,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet!</font>

174
00:10:51,180 --> 00:10:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A strange, powerful visitor decided to 
make his presence felt among their number!</font>

175
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One remarkable individual who flew 
in all the way from America!</font>

176
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He swooped up the American hero 
rankings with his flight Quirk,</font>

177
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">ranking in the top 10 every 
year since his debut!</font>

178
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And his name...</font>

179
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:11,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is Captain Celebrity!</font>

180
00:11:11,850 --> 00:11:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the year since arriving in Japan,</font>

181
00:11:14,950 --> 00:11:17,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he's learned about manly 
ruggedness and Japanese spirit!</font>

182
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:22,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right, this isn't the same 
C.C. we first met a year ago!</font>

183
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:22,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let's go, C.C.!</font>

184
00:11:23,150 --> 00:11:25,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, C.C.!</font>

185
00:11:26,180 --> 00:11:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go, go, C.C.!</font>

186
00:11:29,690 --> 00:11:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C.C.!</font>

187
00:11:32,230 --> 00:11:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's an all-new man!</font>

188
00:11:34,390 --> 00:11:36,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An evolution of invincibility!</font>

189
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After taking Japan as a second home,</font>

190
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:42,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">this soaring superstar is about 
to touch down once again!</font>

191
00:11:42,650 --> 00:11:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Captain Celebrity!</font>

192
00:11:54,420 --> 00:11:55,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Blue 1.</i></font>

193
00:11:55,890 --> 00:11:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We're at the back entrance, and have 
finished deploying to the loading dock.</i></font>

194
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Red 1. We're ready to move.</i></font>

195
00:12:02,870 --> 00:12:05,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Commence operation.</font>

196
00:12:07,790 --> 00:12:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there's my entry pass.</font>

197
00:12:11,710 --> 00:12:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Move out!</font>

198
00:12:14,350 --> 00:12:17,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be making a move on the 
Onomura Pharma Kanto R&D Center.</font>

199
00:12:18,540 --> 00:12:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our target is this research wing, 
on a corner of the property.</font>

200
00:12:21,970 --> 00:12:25,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, that's the Factory's HQ?</font>

201
00:12:25,910 --> 00:12:30,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be launching an investigation on 
the suspicion of producing illegal drugs.</font>

202
00:12:30,580 --> 00:12:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The goal is to secure evidence of 
human experimentation and modifications</font>

203
00:12:33,310 --> 00:12:34,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and any suspects who might be involved.</font>

204
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're just gonna grab anyone 
we can find, then, yeah?</font>

205
00:12:49,540 --> 00:12:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Except...</font>

206
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a chance that the kidnapping 
victims may attack us.</font>

207
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

208
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same type of villain as the one 
from the Christmas incident.</font>

209
00:13:24,180 --> 00:13:27,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this one gonna blow, too?!</font>

210
00:13:27,230 --> 00:13:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If a Quirk causes those explosions...</font>

211
00:13:29,860 --> 00:13:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I can stop it!</font>

212
00:13:33,110 --> 00:13:34,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fatgum, now's your chance!</font>

213
00:13:35,380 --> 00:13:37,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm on it!</font>

214
00:13:52,380 --> 00:13:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So many bomber villains...</font>

215
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:57,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not good! Can I stop them 
all with Erasure at once?!</font>

216
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! Now's our chance!</font>

217
00:14:15,740 --> 00:14:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn, they scared me!</font>

218
00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just raiding the joint, huh?</font>

219
00:14:20,590 --> 00:14:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured they'd show up sooner or later, 
but this is way sooner than I expected.</font>

220
00:14:24,680 --> 00:14:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't have a chance to let 
the research staff escape...</font>

221
00:14:28,340 --> 00:14:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though this makes sure they won't talk.</font>

222
00:14:34,630 --> 00:14:37,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, man, talk about bad timing.</font>

223
00:14:37,620 --> 00:14:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This next plan was just gonna 
be about tormenting C.C.,</font>

224
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:47,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but with my bomber stockpile gone, I'm 
in an "everything must go" situation.</font>

225
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:52,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And on the day of an event 
at the Sky Egg, no less.</font>

226
00:14:55,020 --> 00:14:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, this is gonna be an 
absolute catastrophe.</font>

227
00:15:01,570 --> 00:15:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have something to show all 
my guests here tonight.</font>

228
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? This is my baby, who 
was born just this year!</font>

229
00:15:09,780 --> 00:15:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has my eyes, doesn't he?</font>

230
00:15:12,170 --> 00:15:14,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Takes after his mother 
otherwise, though.</font>

231
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The best of both worlds!</font>

232
00:15:16,650 --> 00:15:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, that picture...</font>

233
00:15:19,730 --> 00:15:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know! Let's get a word 
from my wife, too.</font>

234
00:15:23,170 --> 00:15:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, this is gonna be a surprise, 
so keep quiet, everyone!</font>

235
00:15:29,630 --> 00:15:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hi, honey!</font>

236
00:15:32,570 --> 00:15:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chris? Do you know how late it is?</font>

237
00:15:37,140 --> 00:15:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. Forgot about the time difference.</font>

238
00:15:39,580 --> 00:15:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you asleep?</font>

239
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:43,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The baby finally went to sleep.</font>

240
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:46,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was hoping to do the same, for once...</font>

241
00:15:46,990 --> 00:15:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you need?</font>

242
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, I was talking to 
everyone about you...</font>

243
00:15:51,770 --> 00:15:54,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About me...? And who's everyone?</font>

244
00:15:56,680 --> 00:16:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. Chris! You didn't show the 
picture to anyone, did you?!</font>

245
00:16:00,350 --> 00:16:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one where I look like a mess!</font>

246
00:16:04,900 --> 00:16:08,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I guess it's fine if it's the 
people you're working with over there.</font>

247
00:16:08,870 --> 00:16:10,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like, five or 10 people.</font>

248
00:16:11,930 --> 00:16:13,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Five... right...</font>

249
00:16:13,410 --> 00:16:16,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, is it more than that?</font>

250
00:16:16,260 --> 00:16:20,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you got carried away at a party or 
something and showed it to everybody, didn't you?</font>

251
00:16:20,610 --> 00:16:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You had some event in Tokyo, right? 
Was it at the after-party?</font>

252
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:29,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me the truth. I'll forgive you 
if it was no more than fifty people.</font>

253
00:16:29,890 --> 00:16:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's uh... f-fifty...</font>

254
00:16:33,610 --> 00:16:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that? I didn't hear you.</font>

255
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just... the event 
is still ongoing...</font>

256
00:16:39,550 --> 00:16:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I've got... a crowd 
of fifty thousand.</font>

257
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh... honey? Honey!</font>

258
00:16:51,850 --> 00:16:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's just move onto the 
next segment. Please.</font>

259
00:16:55,070 --> 00:16:55,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roger.</font>

260
00:17:19,820 --> 00:17:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see some wrestling!</font>

261
00:17:21,930 --> 00:17:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

262
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wash!</font>

263
00:17:38,990 --> 00:17:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's almost time for the next segment.</font>

264
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:44,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you check on my boss, Koichi?</font>

265
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:45,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure!</font>

266
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder where the Captain went?</font>

267
00:17:51,070 --> 00:17:53,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe to the lower observation deck?</font>

268
00:17:53,350 --> 00:17:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, the Sky Egg's gift shop! 
I oughta come back here.</font>

269
00:17:58,410 --> 00:18:01,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, there he is! Hey, Captain!</font>

270
00:18:02,550 --> 00:18:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's almost time.</font>

271
00:18:04,610 --> 00:18:07,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. I know, I know, honey.</font>

272
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This was all my fault. And I 
didn't mean to break my promise.</font>

273
00:18:12,650 --> 00:18:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just... I was feeling 
a little proud.</font>

274
00:18:14,990 --> 00:18:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you're right, it 
wasn't just a little.</font>

275
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're completely right. I'm sorry.</font>

276
00:18:22,550 --> 00:18:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We really are high up.</font>

277
00:18:25,870 --> 00:18:28,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh... I wonder what that is?</font>

278
00:18:28,860 --> 00:18:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A fire?</font>

279
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And...</font>

280
00:18:32,590 --> 00:18:35,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think something's headed this way?</font>

281
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:37,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't those—</font>

282
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same villains from Christmas?!</font>

283
00:18:48,700 --> 00:18:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this? Why are we shaking?</font>

284
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An earthquake?</font>

285
00:18:59,080 --> 00:18:59,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy!</font>

286
00:19:18,370 --> 00:19:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all right there, my boy?!</font>

287
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:21,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">J-Just barely!</font>

288
00:19:22,600 --> 00:19:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's more incoming!</font>

289
00:19:25,690 --> 00:19:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No problem! I'm faster and 
stronger than these things!</font>

290
00:19:42,970 --> 00:19:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even your suicide attacks won't cut it!</font>

291
00:19:46,300 --> 00:19:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care how many of you there 
are, I don't see myself losing!</font>

292
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But would you look at that?</font>

293
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:13,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's headed this way!</font>

294
00:20:13,390 --> 00:20:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this one...</font>

295
00:20:16,330 --> 00:20:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">seems way bigger!</font>

296
00:20:20,830 --> 00:20:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Another explosion!</font>

297
00:20:23,120 --> 00:20:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And a huge one, this time!</font>

298
00:20:33,040 --> 00:20:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no...</font>

299
00:20:35,910 --> 00:20:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The tower's in rough shape.</font>

300
00:20:41,910 --> 00:20:43,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the dome—!</font>

301
00:20:47,990 --> 00:20:49,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain, are you okay?!</font>

302
00:20:51,780 --> 00:20:55,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm telling you, my boy, 
this is a piece of cake!</font>

303
00:20:55,660 --> 00:20:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I definitely have my hands full.</font>

304
00:20:59,470 --> 00:21:03,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, as I was saying, when 
the hostages are in danger,</font>

305
00:21:03,740 --> 00:21:06,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all that speed and power 
gets taken off the table...</font>

306
00:21:07,540 --> 00:21:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see what kind of 
fight you put up, now?</font>

307
00:21:10,870 --> 00:21:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come and get me, you lousy villains!</font>

308
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:18,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can endure another one 
or two explosions, easy!</font>

309
00:21:18,770 --> 00:21:21,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's exactly the plan.</font>

310
00:21:21,630 --> 00:21:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, this experiment 
is all about you...</font>

311
00:21:25,930 --> 00:21:29,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, let's start with three hits.</font>

312
00:21:36,780 --> 00:21:42,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't forget the regeneration Quirk my 
cluster bomber's been infused with!</font>

313
00:21:45,490 --> 00:21:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many dynamite punches will it 
take for you to fall, I wonder?!</font>

314
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain—!</font>

315
00:23:25,500 --> 00:23:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always been popular. When I 
became a hero, no one was surprised.</font>

316
00:23:30,170 --> 00:23:33,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I wasn't a real hero. 
Not in the truest sense.</font>

317
00:23:33,840 --> 00:23:35,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time: Balloon Soul.</font>

318
00:23:35,810 --> 00:23:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was empty on the inside... 
until I met you.</font>

